data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful split level home in a great neighborhood! Hardwood floors throughout the entire first floor including the bedrooms.  Ceramic floors in the main Bathroom and Kitchen.  Large living room, eat in kitchen with an Island, nice sized Master bedroom.  3 true Bedrooms upstairs and 1 Bedroom downstairs.  1 full Bathrooms and 1 half Bathroom in the basement (can easily be turned into a full bath since already plumbed).   The basement is partially finished with a large carpeted living area and approximately 400 sq ft of additional space that could be converted to an additional bedroom.  Furnace is NEW (installed in the last year).  All appliances stay including washer and dryer.  Attached Carport.  Amazing fenced in backyard with a deck, patio and privacy trees behind the house.  All vinyl siding.  Easy access to Highways and Amenities.  Neat, clean and immaculate home. Great family home!  Measurements are approximate.
